lead_paragraph: Leicester City will need to know how to break Middlesbrough's defence, midfielder Demarai Gray has said ahead of their next Premier League match on Saturday at the King Power Stadium.

headline.print_headline: Breaking Down Middlesbrough Defence Key, Says Leicester's Gray
